title: Cajun seasoning
ingredients: ['1/2 tablespoon sea salt', '2 teaspoons black pepper, medium ground in pestle', '2 teaspoons white pepper, medium ground in pestle', '1 teaspoon Cayenne pepper', '1 tablespoon paprika', '1 tablespoon dried oregano', '1 tablespoon onion granules', '1 tablespoon garlic granules', '1 teaspoon dried thyme']
